Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 32
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================

Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:34.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It really does look like the drawing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.29,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just the cutest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:52.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We really don't have time for these jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.77,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.05,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,East City!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.68,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You've arrived in East City!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.08,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the latest news on Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.87,Default,Sol2,0000,0000,0000,,He's still on the run?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:31.00,Default,Sol2,0000,0000,0000,,What a persistent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.75,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.49,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's my fault for not paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.07,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You are wearing some unusual attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.01,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not from this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.92,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.20,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.27,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to see the sights?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.88,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much to see in East City, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.98,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just stopped by because I need to switch trains here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.73,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:02.62,Default-alt,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The train at Platform No. 3 is headed for North City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.42,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.32,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me pick up the groceries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.03,Default-alt,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you are planning on riding with us, please board at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.03,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:11.67,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.66,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What a peculiar kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.42,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.99,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,I know I heard footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.79,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.60,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So he was with a middle-aged man with black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.29,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. According to the reports, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.82,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This is where he was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.07,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So he's headed West, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.37,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We have a few injured, some slightly, others seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Scar must be desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.96,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.96,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...he's attracting a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.39,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's head off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.69,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.65,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A funeral, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.76,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't pretty, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:52.65,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,When you get old like me, you can't help but think about when you'll be the one getting buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible thing to say, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I can see, you have a long life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.09,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Grumman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:13.01,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You said we were going to meet in front of Brigadier General Hughes' grave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:19.72,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was something serious since you decided to take the measure of last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:23.37,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,To be doubly sure, I decided to disguise myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:27.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I shouldn't have expected less from you, a man so famous for his eccentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your disguise exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.28,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Eccentric?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.78,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.70,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to find something in the Central Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:49.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't find the midget,\Nwe'll have to search on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can at least find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:58.50,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the entire upper echelon of Central is guilty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:03.49,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But you lost far too much in exchange for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:08.53,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing left if they take away the men you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sir. I can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.32,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Even Raven, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:22.91,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in Central a little while ago, Raven asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:28.26,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you interested in a perfect, immortal army?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Immortal army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.18,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Was he talking about the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.25,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I flat-out rejected him, saying that it was rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.93,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Then soon after,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.35,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I was sent to Eastern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Relegated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:52.79,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I'm now stuck cleaning up after all the messes in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:58.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,More on that topic, do you happen to remember the riot in Lior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:05.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The case where the Fullmetal Alchemist exposed the fake priest of Leto's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.74,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Although Lior was thrown into disarray,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:19.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,the riot was quickly suppressed thanks to the\NEastern Army's rapid response while it was still minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:25.89,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But the Central Army intruded on the scene, and the Eastern Army was withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.81,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:36.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lior's public order suddenly turned for\Nthe worse when the Central Army entered the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.70,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys at Central are really\Nplanning something, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.10,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.73,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Can't things be peaceful until I retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.96,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're the great Lieutenant General Grumman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:57.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you haven't felt satisfied for a second at simply being the head man for a region of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:03.85,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You have the Eastern Army on your side;\Nfull of veteran soldiers who experienced Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:14.61,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I had always thought you'd use that secret contact memo when you needed to whine and beg me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.37,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But you called me here to get me worked up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.44,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.65,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Now that things are getting interesting in Central,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:30.13,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,the flame of ambition in my heart has been lit once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too serious or your makeup will be ruined, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.71,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, would you like to join me for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.64,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.79,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the invitation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't this place have any good books on Eastern Alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:12.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll just visit Xing and study there instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but there's no way I'll be able to cross that desert with my automail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.51,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,M-Major! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:35.84,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.38,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be quiet in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:45.58,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're after a girl from Xing\Nwho carries around a black and white cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.31,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.10,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today on the Colonel's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.71,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she's headed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:03.61,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,According to a witness, she was in\NEast City and was headed north from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,North, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. If we know that much, it's safe to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the Colonel I said thanks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.23,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.25,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.22,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.69,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter of introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.16,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It may not do you much good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.16,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,but you should meet her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Meet who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.63,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,She resides even farther north than the Northern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:40.34,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,A general who guards the Drakma border and holds another name, the "Northern Wall of Briggs"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.66,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,...Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.67,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.70,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run, Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.80,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Report this to Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.03,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,That train is headed for West City!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:45.76,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really find much on Eastern Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:57.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May's long-distance transmutation was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could use that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:04.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I should have asked her about it when she was still at Dr. Nox's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ling said that it's used predominantly for medical purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:19.99,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Fullmetal Alchemist's little brother who wears a giant suit wherever he goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.87,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.86,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:27.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to keep it down. We're in a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.87,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:35.02,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,What are you studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.98,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's a form of alchemy used in Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.99,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Xing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:53.57,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you Elric Brothers skilled enough to be state qualified in Amestris, a nation so advanced in alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.54,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you researching minor forms of alchemy used in other countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:07.64,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't exactly say, "I'm looking for a way to get my body back and fight Homunculi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:14.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Eastern Alchemy is used predominantly for medical purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:20.26,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm researching to see if there are any other ways human lives could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.59,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Nothing less to be expected from the Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Get your things together! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you have to keep it down in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the hotel and pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whose brat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.93,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,If you're his brother, it must mean you're Edward, the State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.77,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.28,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,So the rumors were true! You really are a tiny alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're up for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to blast you to Neptune?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.95,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.88,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,So they were right! You get really angry when people say you're short!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.66,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Back away from Sir Selim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.84,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you're Selim Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.73,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to be headed north?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it was my choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.71,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:44.33,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,This boy has admired you for so long, Mr. Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Admired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like alchemy, Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.58,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:56.54,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to learn alchemy and become a State Alchemist like Mr. Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Admired me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.22,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:01.10,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I want to be useful to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love your Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:11.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...Führer President King Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.49,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.87,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very noble man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:21.51,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He perseveres through hard work that would make a normal person cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:25.00,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,...and works every day with only one thing in mind: the well-being of his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President {\i1}does{\i0\fscx20} {\r} seem busy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.16,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.68,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He still plans on working to his fullest in active service.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:42.73,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I'm constantly telling him to retire already, bearing his age in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.81,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been someone totally committed to his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:53.19,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He can do his job, but he's always been a blockhead when it comes to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:57.83,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He was so impolite; I gave him a good slap across the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.60,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's where it all started. Then, we started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.75,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,And our first date was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.57,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.04,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to talk about senseless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.27,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:20.97,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.83,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.75,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.86,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Why the surprise visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:32.80,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I had some rare free time, so I came to see your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:38.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I heard the Fullmetal Alchemist was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.71,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We just saw each other at Central Headquarters, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.59,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you met each other at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.78,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.97,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you trying to say that we don't look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We're not connected by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:12.01,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,We were never able to have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.49,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,So we adopted him from a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.68,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He grew up to become a kind boy who cares so much for his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.24,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.04,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.94,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.92,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:41.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just that we only see you when you're working at Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.65,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just... right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're just stunned to see such a different side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.14,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.35,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.15,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.90,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a bit different from your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.60,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving already, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.33,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's about time for me to return to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.72,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.22,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.75,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.54,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:05.68,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think his wife or son know that he's a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to head north! All the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:19.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get a hold of that midget and\Nmake her tell us the secret behind Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.65,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.78,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.91,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:52.41,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you let them get away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.77,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of the West, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.16,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.86,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,He was last seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:06.97,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.06,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,And this is West City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.24,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Scar and Marcoh disappeared somewhere in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:22.52,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,A train must slow down significantly at a curve, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.93,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible for someone to jump off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.14,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say it's impossible, but it's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.24,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:37.14,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I wonder which direction they ran after they jumped off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.13,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,North...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...or south...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:38.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be our first time traveling north?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be able to see snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:43.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Snow, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:47.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it rarely stuck to the ground in Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.83,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The cat and the mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:04.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Insanity and hatred clash in a white world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:09.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The fiercest battle yet opens the gate to a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:15.26,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:19.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 33, The Northern Wall of Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:24.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her golden hair is a flame made of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
